nings":["Altered form of English   Pelham  ."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Pelham was born in 1264, in Sussex, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Eve Stopham. He died in 1346, in his hometown, at the age of 82."},"et":{"1264–1346":"1264–1346","1262–Female":"1262–Surnud","1289–Female":"1289–Surnud","1346":"1346","1289":"1289","1264":"1264","1262":"1262","abt 1289":"umbes 1289","Angermaning, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1264–1346":"1264–1346","1262–Female":"1262–Kuollut","1289–Female":"1289–Kuollut","1346":"1346","1289":"1289","1264":"1264","1262":"1262","abt 1289":"noin 1289","Angermaning, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1264–1346":"1264–1346","1262–Female":"1262–Décédée","1289–Female":"1289–Décédée","1346":"1346","1289":"1289","1264":"1264","1262":"1262","abt 1289":"environ 1289","Angermaning, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"John Pelham est né en 1264, à Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Eve Stopham. Il est décédé en 1346, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 82 ans."},"de":{"1264–1346":"1264–1346","1262–Female":"1262–Verstorben","1289–Female":"1289–Verstorben","1346":"1346","1289":"1289","1264":"1264","1262":"1262","abt 1289":"um 1289","Angermaning, Sussex, England":"Sussex, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"John Pelham wurde 1264 in Sussex, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Eve Stopham mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb 1346 im Alter von 82 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1264–1346":"1264–1346","1262–Female":"1262–Desede","1289–Female":"1289–Desede","1346":"1346","1289":"1289","1264":"1264","1262":"1262","abt 1289":"about 1289","Angermaning, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu